# Epic 6: Frontend-Backend Integration
**Status:** Depends on Epic 4 & 5 | **Arch Ref:** Section 3 (Polling)

## Technical Blueprint
- **Sync Strategy:** Aggressive Polling.
- **URL Standard:** Use relative paths (`/api/items`) to leverage Nginx proxy.

## Stories & Specs
### 6.1 Polling Engine
- **Action:** `setInterval(fetchItems, 3000)`.
- **AC:** UI refreshes list without user interaction.

### 6.2 POST Integration
- **Action:** Wire "Add" button to `fetch('/api/items', {method: 'POST'})`.
- **AC:** Form submission adds item to database.
